<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2083] Problem with Distributed SpellCheck</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2083</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In DistributedSpellCheckTest, if I add 10 additional documents to the index with field &quot;lowerfilt&quot; containing &quot;The quack red fox jumped over the lazy brown dogs.&quot;, then the shard&apos;ed SpellCheckComponent wants to correct &quot;quick&quot; to &quot;quack&quot;.  The control, non-shared&apos;ed component correctly does not try to correct &quot;quick&quot;.  The test subsequently fails.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12472291">SOLR-2083</key>
            <summary>Problem with Distributed SpellCheck</summary>
